name: Amarok Multimedia
tag_list: cd-duplication, dvd-duplication, cd-replication, dvd-replication, cd-printing, dvd-printing, duplication, replication, pressing, copying, usb-stick, flash-drive
overview:
Amarok are UK providers of CD and DVD duplication, replication and print services.

Amarok provide a comprehensive range of CD & DVD duplication, replication and print facilities. Amarok offer a comprehensive range of packaging for CDs and DVDs including printed card packaging such as full colour Card Wallets, Lancing Packs and Digipacks. Amarok also provide fast turnaround services for emergency requirements and have a huge in-house capacity to duplicate and print thousands of CDs or DVDs in a day. Amarok also provide USB flash drives / memory sticks with optional on body printing and duplication.
